<text>Restrain

&lt; Previous | Index | Next &gt;

The restrain command restrains the currently selected particles with a harmonic spring with a specific force constant, at their current positions. (To see how to restrain atoms without using scripts, see this section.)

Syntax:

restrain [force constant]

where [force constant] is a non-negative number that will be the force constant of the harmonic spring.

Here is an example of using the restrain command to set the restraints on selected atoms.

 
 
